CELEBRATING VICTORY OF GOOD OVER EVIL

Gulshan Kumar and T-Series present
A T-Series Films and Retrophiles production

snippet.description:
If you liked the Video don’t forget to Like, Share and Subscribe.

Hey Guys, 
Welcome to my Youtube Channel,
I'm Jonathan Amaral, you might know me as Jonathan Gaming.
I started my professional Esports Career competing in Pubg Mobile Championships (Now BGMI),
Since the start of my career, I have been consistent with my gameplay and always been working hard to achieve my goals via winning Domestic/Global Championships. 
"The only player you should try to be better than is the player you were yesterday."
I Stream BGMI regularly, I also enjoy playing Valorant and other fun games once in a while!
I upload videos regarding Tutorials for BGMI, Funny Highlights, Intense Fights, Crate Openings, Vlogs, etc.

snippet.title: निर्जला एकादशी व्रत कथा || Nirjala Ekadashi Vrat Katha || एकादशी की कथा
snippet.description:
निर्जला एकादशी व्रत कथा || Nirjala Ekadashi Vrat Katha || एकादशी की कथा
Today on 30 May 2023, We are presenting the video of Nirjala Ekadashi Ki Katha. 
Nirjala Ekadashi is one of the most popular ekadashi among all the ekadashis. Nirjala Ekadashi is celebrated on the eleventh day of Shukla paksh in Jyestha month. In this Nirjala Ekadashi vrat katha video we have show the complete nirjala ekadashi vrat katha mentioned in puran and also the lok katha of Nirjala ekadashi. Nirjala ekadashi is also known as Bhim Ekadashi, Bhimsen ekadashi, Pandav nirjala ekadashi or bhim gyaras in y.  you may be wondering nirjala ekadashi kab hai ? nirjala ekadashi 2023 is on May 30 2023. Let us watch Nirjala Ekadashi ki katha and pray to lord visnhu to bless us all.
ज्येष्ठ मास में शुक्ल पक्ष में जो एकादशी हो, उसका  पूरी निष्ठा से निर्जल व्रत करो। केवल कुल्ला या आचमन करने के लिये मुख में जल डाल सकते हो, उसको छोड़कर और किसी प्रकार का जल विद्वान् मनुष्य मुख में न डाले, अन्यथा व्रत भंग हो जाता है। एकादशी को सूर्योदय से लेकर दूसरे दिन के सूर्योदय तक मनुष्य जल का त्याग करे तो यह व्रत पूर्ण होता है। अगले दिन द्वादशी को निर्मल प्रभातकाल में स्नान करके ब्राह्मणों तथा जरूरतमंदों को यथाशक्ति दान करे। इस प्रकार सब कार्य पूरा करके भोजन करे। वर्षभर में जितनी एकादशियाँ होती हैं, उन सबका फल निर्जला एकादशी के सेवन से मनुष्य प्राप्त कर लेता है; इसमें  कोई सन्देह नहीं है। शंख, चक्र और गदा धारण करने वाले भगवान् केशव ने मुझसे कहा था कि ‘यदि मानव सब कुछ छोड़कर मेरी शरण में आ जाय और एकादशी को निराहार रहे तो वह सब पापों से छूट जाता है।’
एकादशी व्रत करने वाले मनुष्य के पास विशालकाय, विकराल आकृति और काले रंग वाले दण्ड-पाशधारी भयंकर यमदूत नहीं जाते। अन्तकाल में पीताम्बरधारी, सौम्य स्वभाव वाले, हाथ में सुदर्शन धारण करने वाले और मन के समान वेगशाली विष्णु दूत आकर इस वैष्णव पुरुष को भगवान् विष्णु के धाम में ले जाते हैं। अतः निर्जला एकादशी को पूर्ण यत्न करके उपवास करना चाहिये। तुम भी सब पापों की शान्ति के लिये यत्न के साथ उपवास और श्रीहरि का पूजन करो। स्त्री हो या पुरुष, यदि उसने मेरु पर्वत के बराबर भी महान् पाप किया हो तो वह सब एकादशी के प्रभाव से भस्म हो जाता है। जो मनुष्य उस दिन जल के नियम का पालन करता है, वह पुण्य का भागी होता है, उसे एक-एक पहर में कोटि-कोटि स्वर्ण मुद्रा दान करने का फल प्राप्त होता सुना गया है। मनुष्य निर्जला एकादशी के दिन स्नान, दान, जप, होम आदि जो कुछ भी करता है, वह सब अक्षय होता है, यह भगवान् श्रीकृष्ण का कथन है।

#निर्जला एकादशी #NirjalaEkadashi #EkadashiVratKatha #एकादशी  #PandavEkadashiKatha

एकादशी व्रत करने वाले मनुष्य के पास विशालकाय, विकराल आकृति और काले रंग वाले दण्ड-पाशधारी भयंकर यमदूत नहीं जाते। अन्तकाल में पीताम्बरधारी, सौम्य स्वभाव वाले, हाथ में सुदर्शन धारण करने वाले और मन के समान वेगशाली विष्णु दूत आकर इस वैष्णव पुरुष को भगवान् विष्णु के धाम में ले जाते हैं। अतः निर्जला एकादशी को पूर्ण यत्न करके उपवास करना चाहिये। तुम भी सब पापों की शान्ति के लिये यत्न के साथ उपवास और श्रीहरि का पूजन करो। स्त्री हो या पुरुष, यदि उसने मेरु पर्वत के बराबर भी महान् पाप किया हो तो वह सब एकादशी के प्रभाव से भस्म हो जाता है। जो मनुष्य उस दिन जल के नियम का पालन करता है, वह पुण्य का भागी होता है, उसे एक-एक पहर में कोटि-कोटि स्वर्ण मुद्रा दान करने का फल प्राप्त होता सुना गया है। मनुष्य निर्जला एकादशी के दिन स्नान, दान, जप, होम आदि जो कुछ भी करता है, वह सब अक्षय होता है, यह भगवान् श्रीकृष्ण का कथन है।

#निर्जला एकादशी #NirjalaEkadashi #EkadashiVratKatha #एकादशी  #PandavEkadashiKatha

snippet.title: Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 09 Teaser - 30th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 09 Teaser - 30th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Imran Abbas as Shani
Neelam Muneer as Shanzay
Nimra Khan as Sajeela
Mahmood Aslam as Kamran
Ismat Zaidi as Kulsoom
Maira Khan as Nadiya
Zainab Qayoom as Samiya
Saqib Sameer as Khawar
Aadi Khan as Jugnu
Birjees Farooqui as Farzana
Farah Nadeem as Shakeela
Kinza Bukhari as Shazia
Mirza Rizwan as Faiq

#EhraameJunoon 
#NeelamMuneer 
#ImranAbbas

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3784 | 30 May 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3784: Ek Ghante Ki Meeting
--------------------------------------------------------
To meet Sapna and Kalpana, everyone gets ready, and Popatlal offers his greetings to God for sending 'rishtas' for him. Popatlal prays that Kalpana and Sapna should not get to know about his other name. He welcomes Chamapaklal and Mahila Mandal at his house for help.  Pyaarelal is delighted to meet Sapna. Could Pyaarelal's life be altered by this encounter? Will Pyarelal get married this time? Watch the episode to know more.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3784, 30 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 07 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream - 29th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 08 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Nimra Khan - 30th May 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 08 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Nimra Khan - 30th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Imran Abbas as Shani
Neelam Muneer as Shanzay
Nimra Khan as Sajeela
Mahmood Aslam as Kamran
Ismat Zaidi as Kulsoom
Maira Khan as Nadiya
Zainab Qayoom as Samiya
Saqib Sameer as Khawar
Aadi Khan as Jugnu
Birjees Farooqui as Farzana
Farah Nadeem as Shakeela
Kinza Bukhari as Shazia
Mirza Rizwan as Faiq

Episode 3783: Do Do Rishte
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak ultimately succeeds in getting a leave of absence from work, but his manager is still interested in Pyaarelal's tale. Taarak explains to his boss why Pyaarelal, a.k.a. Popatlal, has been single and how being single has made his life miserable. Taarak's manager understands and gives him permission to go a little early. When Pyaarelal learns that his friend Taarak is returning, he is delighted. Champaklal is one of the elderly people, thus the Gokuldham women and Pyaarelel thought to invite him to the meeting. Pyaarelal receives a call later about another marriage proposal, but the bride's family prefers his original name, Popatlal. Now, what will he do?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3783, 29 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 700 & 701 | Recap
snippet.description:
Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 700 & 701 | Recap

Ekam confronts Nehmat and forces the truth out of her. He blames Jasmine for ruining his life and vows to exact his revenge on her. Meanwhile, Renuka overhears Sartaj's conversation with the doctor and promises to keep Nehmat's pregnancy a secret. Will she keep her word?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | Kya Karie Korimol | ALIF x Aashima Mahajan x Noor Mohammad
snippet.description:
A father-daughter relationship envelops immense compassion, protection, and love. They share a special connection that grows stronger with time and never fades away. #KyaKarieKorimol unveils such a beautiful father-daughter bond on a wedding day. The lyrics tell the emotional journey of a bride and her father as they prepare for her wedding feast.

Featuring Alif, a poet, singer, and songwriter who won the IRAA Award for his single ‘Like A Sufi’, his poignant and melancholic lyrical compositions are known for their colloquial references to society.

He’s accompanied by the very soulful Aashima Mahajan, a well-known Indian musician, playback singer, and actor & Noor Mohammad, an Indian traditional Sufi music performer and songwriter from Handwara in North Kashmir.

Tune in to this masterpiece to get a glimpse of a father-daughter love.

ALIF x Aashima Mahajan x Noor Mohammad

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.
